{
  "text": "We present the results in Tables 3 broken down by work experience as formulated in equation [CITATION_1] . In the table results in panel A are derived from a wage equation including in addition to year, cohort and work experience fixed effects 27 In order to conserve space only the results for the decomposition estimation results are presented. For more details see [CITATION_2] .",
